thread.title: Noelene Stefani
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Noelene Stefani

author: Noelene Stefani
title: Noelene Stefani
text:
I found Peter and Celeste easy and comfortable to deal with questions asked were answered.Peter didn't overdo the sales pitch to me and after talking to many agents found this refreshing.Celeste I could talk girl stuff to in relation to the house and she made me feel comfortable in any decisions made.Selling my home after 36years was a big deal for me and they both helped me to go through the process with ease.I would recommend them both they make a great team.
Noelene Stefani
